## Notes

* This passive ability applies a stacking Resonance counter to the target on hit (anything above a Graze). Upon clear (when the Monk activates [Resonant Touch](/resonantTouchDeadfire/)), all counters in an AoE are cleared and deal 15 [Raw Damage](/rawDamage/) each. Targets out of range retain their current stack.
